  <brief_title>Valsartan and Amlodipine Compared to Losartan and Amlodipine in Hypertensive Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Antihypertensive Activity of Valsartan and Amlodipine Compared to Losartan and Amlodipine Through Ambulatory Blood Pressure Monitoring in Moderate Hypertensive Patients in a Randomized, Controlled, Double-Blind Study</official_title>
